12:32.440 --> 12:36.760
because I think all three of them could, you know, really improve.

12:36.760 --> 12:42.400
And it all being their debut season, I think we could see some proper improvements,

12:42.400 --> 12:46.900
and we could see quite some battles for who's the best female driver on track,

12:46.960 --> 12:52.180
but also proving that they can race and they can be on the pace with the boys.

12:52.680 --> 12:56.300
Definitely, and I feel like we need to also talk about some of the other guys in the field.

12:56.300 --> 13:03.980
Rocco Coronel, again, he was quite unlucky at times, but he was very much another driver who's all or nothing.

13:03.980 --> 13:07.840
