13:20.820 --> 13:25.800
Yeah, I feel like he had the same problem as Luna, which, you know, is a bit disappointing to,

13:25.800 --> 13:31.740
as I've said with Luna, kind of, you know, not manage it on that one circuit where it really matters.

13:31.740 --> 13:37.420
