14:36.920 --> 14:50.120
And I feel like you see them try out more stupid stuff around here, because they know you can try something which is like, in the main series, you'd think, “hey, maybe I shouldn't try that, because maybe it won't work out.”

14:50.120 --> 14:57.180
But, you know, I feel like here's the opportunity to really throw out stuff, because, you know, even if you maybe don't win the championship, it'll be fine.

14:57.420 --> 15:02.980
And it's really good to see them be able to gain that experience and make their first impressions.

15:02.980 --> 15:13.440
Yeah, so alongside the EC4 Winter, we also had the EC3 championship Winter Series, which exact same calendar, it’s very much the parent series in a way.

15:13.600 --> 15:32.040
