31:43.720 --> 31:46.220
She was by far the best Rodin.

31:46.780 --> 31:51.620
With Ella Lloyd qualifying P10 and Ella Stephens qualifying P11.

31:51.620 --> 31:57.160
And Ella Lloyd is kind of considered the biggest title favorite just from, you know, stats.

31:57.160 --> 31:59.760
