32:10.100 --> 32:15.240
And the Rodin did not seem to get alive for both allies.

32:15.240 --> 32:17.800
But for Emma, it sure as hell did.

32:17.800 --> 32:22.480
Because P3 was really, really solid in the sprint race.

32:22.480 --> 32:27.280
She was, like, pretty much the only one in the front who did any big overtakes.

32:27.280 --> 32:31.740
And, I mean, she did it on, I think it was Ferreira and Westcott.

32:31.740 --> 32:35.280
