32:51.020 --> 32:52.720
But Alba had a really great start.

32:52.720 --> 32:54.900
Until the point where Alba made a mistake.

32:54.900 --> 32:57.960
Which, you know, Emma just did not make.

32:57.960 --> 33:02.400
