33:10.060 --> 33:12.220
She was, she did everything she could.

33:12.220 --> 33:16.120
And she made every point, in my opinion, that she could have made.

33:16.120 --> 33:20.740
So I think she was, for me, by far the biggest, you know, winner this weekend.

33:20.740 --> 33:24.860
And even last season, I felt like people really underrated her.

33:25.180 --> 33:31.760
And I think everyone talked about, it's going to be a championship fight between Ella Lloyd, Alisha Palmowski, and Alba Larson.

33:31.760 --> 33:36.440
