33:40.140 --> 33:43.960
I think Ella Lloyd and Alisha Palmowski are pretty evenly matched up.

33:43.960 --> 33:47.520
And Alba Larsson and Emma Felbermayrare also pretty evenly matched up.

33:47.520 --> 33:53.460
If we look back at last season, Emma Felbermayr, technically she won twice, but one time was disqualified.

33:53.460 --> 33:56.380
