34:15.360 --> 34:17.340
Which is, I mean, P8 is alright.

34:17.340 --> 34:22.690
But if your teammate qualifies P2, can you really be happy about that?

34:22.690 --> 34:25.080
I mean, she won the sprint race.

34:25.140 --> 34:28.670
And she was kind of solid in the feature race.

34:28.670 --> 34:31.760
Doing some overtakes and keeping L.A Lloyd behind her.

34:31.760 --> 34:38.580
But I was not as convinced by her as I had hoped to be convinced by her.

34:38.580 --> 34:40.940
So we already talked about also.

34:40.940 --> 34:45.760
Ella Lloyd, I think, was the big let down from what people expected of her.

34:45.760 --> 34:51.920
Because, you know, she is really the highest rookie from last season.

34:52.300 --> 34:54.710
And I also expected her to do better.

34:54.710 --> 34:57.920
But in Shanghai, Rodin also struggled last season.

34:57.920 --> 35:02.190
