35:32.860 --> 35:35.820
I think I really agree with Robertson and Ava Dobson.

35:35.820 --> 35:38.600
Because both of them are at Hitech, right?

35:38.600 --> 35:39.170
Yeah.

35:39.170 --> 35:43.400
