35:43.400 --> 35:46.100
Hitech pretty much struggled to score a point.

35:46.320 --> 35:47.660
Like, the whole season through.

35:47.660 --> 35:48.340
This year.

35:48.340 --> 35:50.300
You know, Ava qualified.

35:50.300 --> 35:51.280
I think it was P9.

35:51.280 --> 35:56.190
You know, Rachel, who's not quite, you know, in the top ten.

35:56.190 --> 35:58.040
I think she was like P12 or P13.

35:58.040 --> 35:59.540
Which is still fine.

35:59.540 --> 36:02.380
But both did really, really well in the races.

36:02.380 --> 36:06.920
I think Dobson finished P9 or P10 or something in the sprint.

36:06.920 --> 36:08.880
And P10 in the main race.

36:08.940 --> 36:09.980
It's really, really solid.

36:09.980 --> 36:14.230
And more importantly, beside what you mentioned with the crash into She-Way.

36:14.230 --> 36:17.670
