36:26.900 --> 36:30.730
Because Dobson also raced pretty hard against Ella Lloyd.

36:30.730 --> 36:34.540
Who, you know, I expected to obviously be able to take it pretty fast.

36:34.540 --> 36:36.440
Just with her experience and speed and stuff.

36:36.440 --> 36:38.690
And Ava being in the Hitech.

36:38.860 --> 36:41.520
But it seems to me that both the drivers are an improvement.

36:41.520 --> 36:43.260
And the team has made the step up.

36:43.260 --> 36:47.540
And it's great to see another team that will most likely be able to finish on points.

36:47.540 --> 36:48.660
Quite a few times.

36:48.660 --> 36:51.170
And maybe take points from some drivers.

36:51.170 --> 36:52.060
Yeah.

36:52.060 --> 36:55.560
Especially as like as in for Hitech being in their second year.

36:55.560 --> 36:58.360
And I didn't really have much expectations for them last year.

36:58.360 --> 37:02.690
That it was great to see that they were actually battling and fighting for points.

37:02.690 --> 37:03.560
Yeah.

37:03.560 --> 37:05.690
Who else do we have?

37:05.690 --> 37:07.660
We have Bruce.

37:07.780 --> 37:10.500
I think qualifying was kind of disappointing.

37:10.500 --> 37:15.380
