37:19.900 --> 37:20.880
Who else do we have?

37:21.440 --> 37:24.920
Kosterman was generally, to me, a bit disappointing.

37:24.920 --> 37:28.400
Because, like, even Gademan still got PA'd.

37:28.400 --> 37:32.660
She was a bit unlucky in the feature race to be hit by Jade Jacquet.

37:32.660 --> 37:37.100
Generally, in a sprint race, she had quite the gap up front.

37:37.100 --> 37:40.940
And couldn't really manage to stay on the same pace as the rest of the grid.

37:41.040 --> 37:44.320
So, that was kind of, you know, not the greatest thing.

37:44.320 --> 37:48.710
And ART is, I think, kind of the backmarker team this year.

37:48.710 --> 37:51.860
